### Plant Shop API HTTP Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/health

### Get All Plants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants

### Get Plant by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/1

### Get Plant by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/name/Monstera%20Deliciosa

### Search Plants by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?name=Plant

### Search Plants by Scientific Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?scientificName=deliciosa

### Search Plants by Price Range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?minPrice=20&maxPrice=50

### Get Plants In Stock Only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?inStockOnly=true

### Create New Plant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Golden Pothos",
  "scientificName": "Epipremnum aureum 'Golden'",
  "price": 19.99,
  "stockQuantity": 35
}

### Create Another Plant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Parlor Palm",
  "scientificName": "Chamaedorea elegans",
  "price": 29.50,
  "stockQuantity": 20
}

### Update Plant (Full Update)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/plants/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monstera Deliciosa",
  "scientificName": "Monstera deliciosa",
  "price": 49.99,
  "stockQuantity": 30
}

### Update Plant Stock Only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/plants/2/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stockQuantity": 45
}

### Get Plant Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/stats

### Delete Plant
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/plants/15

### Test Validation - Invalid Plant (Negative Price)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Plant",
  "scientificName": "Invalidus testus",
  "price": -10.00,
  "stockQuantity": 5
}

### Test Validation - Invalid Plant (Empty Name)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "scientificName": "Invalidus testus",
  "price": 25.00,
  "stockQuantity": 5
}

### Test Validation - Duplicate Plant Name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monstera Deliciosa",
  "scientificName": "Monstera deliciosa duplicate",
  "price": 40.00,
  "stockQuantity": 10
}

### Update Non-existent Plant (404 Error)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/plants/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Non-existent Plant",
  "scientificName": "Nonexistus testus",
  "price": 25.00,
  "stockQuantity": 5
}

### Delete Non-existent Plant (404 Error)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/plants/999

### Update Stock with Negative Value (400 Error)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/plants/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stockQuantity": -5
}

### Complex Search - Multiple Parameters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?name=Plant&minPrice=15&maxPrice=60&inStockOnly=true

### Search with No Results
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/search?name=NonExistentPlant

### Get Non-existent Plant by ID (404 Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/999

### Get Non-existent Plant by Name (404 Error)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plants/name/NonExistentPlant
